cmo9umgqz0001v0nn0n184pp7	\N	PROBATION	<!-- x-tinymce/html --><p>We are delighted to formally confirm your employment for the role of&nbsp; <strong>-designation-</strong>, which will commence on <strong>-confirmation date-.</strong></p>\n<p>Your current CTC is&nbsp; <strong>INR -CTC-</strong></p>\n<p>Enclosed herewith, you will find a comprehensive breakdown of your salary details. It is important to note that your salary will be subject to periodic reviews in accordance with the company's policies related to your role. Any adjustments will be based on your satisfactory performance. The remaining terms and conditions of your employment will remain unchanged.<br><br>Congratulations on this significant step in your career! We eagerly anticipate the valuable contributions you will bring, and we extend our best wishes for success in this new endeavour.</p>	/uploads/pdfs/probation_1776850018053.pdf	f	2026-04-22 09:26:58.372	\N	{"ctc": 0, "dob": "", "hra": 0, "pan": "", "city": "", "date": "", "grat": 0, "mode": "Office", "name": "Mr. poorna", "spec": 0, "basic": 0, "email": "m@fingrow.in", "state": "", "gender": "Male", "hraPct": "50", "mobile": "", "prefix": "Mr.", "reason": "", "aadhaar": "", "address": "", "country": "India", "empType": "Full-time", "manager": "", "pinCode": "", "sigName": "", "address1": "", "address2": "", "basicPct": "40", "duration": "3", "exitType": "Resigned", "lastName": "", "location": "th", "passport": "", "reviewer": "", "altMobile": "", "firstName": "poorna", "incAmount": "", "offerDate": "", "transport": 19200, "validTill": "", "currentCtc": "", "deductions": "0", "department": "Engineering", "exitReason": "", "fatherName": "", "revisedCtc": "", "assetReturn": "Completed", "designation": "Finance Manager", "finalAmount": "0", "gratuityPct": "4.81", "hrClearance": "Yes", "itClearance": "Yes", "joiningDate": "", "offerExpiry": "", "reviewNotes": "", "noticePeriod": "30", "noticeServed": "Yes", "probationEnd": "2026-08-28", "workLocation": "t