ation, I will return all company property and that the property will be returned in proper working order. I understand I may be held financially responsible for lost or damaged property. This agreement includes, but is not limited to, laptops, cell phones and other equipment. I understand that failure to return equipment will be considered theft and may lead to criminal prosecution by Company.\n\nI accept all the terms and conditions mentioned therein. I shall commence my Internship with effect from __________________\n\nName:                                                                             Date:                                                Signature:</div>	/uploads/pdfs/offer_1777372775539.pdf	f	2026-04-28 10:39:35.809	cmoiesezp0000zaah9tn63l93	{"ctc": 6898, "dob": "", "pan": "", "city": "", "date": "", "grat": 130.2122365684235, "mode": "Office", "name": "Mr. mpc m", "spec": 2707.115105372631, "basic": 2707.115105372631, "email": "m45@gmail.com", "state": "", "gender": "Male", "hraPct": "50", "mobile": "", "prefix": "Mr.", "reason": "", "aadhaar": "", "address": "", "country": "India", "empType": "Full-time", "manager": "", "pinCode": "", "sigName": "", "address1": "", "address2": "", "basicPct": "40", "duration": "3", "exitType": "Resigned", "lastName": "mpc m", "location": "", "passport": "", "reviewer": "", "altMobile": "", "firstName": "Mr.", "incAmount": "", "includePT": "No", "offerDate": "", "validTill": "", "currentCtc": "", "deductions": "0", "department": "", "exitReason": "", "fatherName": "", "includeEPF": "Yes", "includeESI": "Yes", "revisedCtc": "6898", "assetReturn": "Completed", "designation": "software engineering", "finalAmount": "0", "gratuityPct": "4.81", "hrClearance": "Yes", "itClearance": "Yes", "joiningDate": "", "offerExpiry": "", "reviewNotes": "", "monthlyGross": 563.9823136192981, "noticePeriod": "30", "noticeServed": "Yes", "probationEnd": "", "workLocation": "", "confirmStatus": "Confirmed", "effectiveDate": "", "incPerce