ation, I will return all company property and that the property will be returned in proper working order. I understand I may be held financially responsible for lost or damaged property. This agreement includes, but is not limited to, laptops, cell phones and other equipment. I understand that failure to return equipment will be considered theft and may lead to criminal prosecution by Company.\n\nI accept all the terms and conditions mentioned therein. I shall commence my Internship with effect from __________________\n\nName:                                                                             Date:                                                Signature:</div>	/uploads/pdfs/offer_1777377477038.pdf	f	2026-04-28 11:57:58.466	cmoiig32r000461xxy1vwraim	{"ctc": 3456, "dob": "", "pan": "", "city": "h", "date": "2026-04-30", "grat": 65.23825595541777, "mode": "Office", "name": "poorna", "spec": 1356.304697617833, "basic": 1356.304697617833, "email": "m87@gmail.com", "state": "h", "gender": "Male", "hraPct": "50", "mobile": "234567", "prefix": "Mr.", "reason": "", "aadhaar": "", "address": "h, h, 5678", "country": "India", "empType": "Full-time", "manager": "", "pinCode": "5678", "sigName": "g", "address1": "", "address2": "", "basicPct": "40", "duration": "3", "exitType": "Resigned", "lastName": "", "location": "", "passport": "", "reviewer": "", "altMobile": "", "firstName": "poorna", "incAmount": "", "includePT": "No", "offerDate": "2026-04-29", "validTill": "2026-04-29", "currentCtc": "", "deductions": "0", "department": "Operations", "exitReason": "", "fatherName": "", "includeEPF": "Yes", "includeESI": "Yes", "revisedCtc": "3456", "assetReturn": "Completed", "designation": "HR Manager", "finalAmount": "0", "gratuityPct": "4.81", "hrClearance": "Yes", "itClearance": "Yes", "joiningDate": "2026-04-15", "offerExpiry": "2026-04-29", "reviewNotes": "", "monthlyGross": 282.5634786703819, "noticePeriod": "30", "noticeServed": "Yes", "probationEnd": "", "workLocatio