cmojkw6lv0001h7gaw7okhjc5	\N	OFFER	Congratulations! We are excited to offer you the opportunity to join our internship program.\n\nThis internship will have an initial duration of <b>-duration-</b> Month(s), commencing on or before <b>-effective_from-</b>, and will conclude on <b>-effective_to-</b>. The extension of this internship or transition to a permanent role will be contingent upon your performance and our business needs.<b>\nStipend:&nbsp;</b><div>-stipend-&nbsp; You will receive a monthly stipend during the duration of your internship, payable at the end of each month.&nbsp;</div><div>Joining Details:\n\nDate of Joining: On or before -effective_from-.\nLocation: -location-.\nDesignation: -designation-\nRequired Documents:\n\nCopy of your highest educational qualification certificate.\nIdentification and address proof (any one of the following: Passport, Aadhar Card, Voter ID).\nTerms of Internship:\n\nTermination: The internship may be terminated by either party with a given notice of 15 days in writing or via email.\nValidity: The internship agreement is valid until the end date specified ( -effective_to- ), with the possibility of renewal or extension based on mutual agreement.\nWe hope that you will find your internship with us enriching and rewarding. We look forward to having you as part of our team and are confident that this will be an exceptional opportunity for professional growth and personal development.&nbsp;Kindly confirm your acceptance of this offer on or before the joining date -<b>date</b>-.\n\nThank you for considering this opportunity, and we eagerly anticipate your affirmative reply.\n\nWith best wishes,\nFor -company name-\n\n-Hr Name-\n-Signatory Designation-\n\nCandidate Undertaking:\n\nI have carefully read and understood the terms and conditions mentioned above.\n\nI acknowledge that while I am working for -company name-, I will take proper care of all company equipment that I am entrusted with. I further understand that upon termination, I will return all company property and that the property will be returned in proper working order. I understand I may be held financially responsible for lost or damaged property. This agreement includes, but is not limited to, laptops, cell phones and other equipment. I understand that failure to return equipment will be considered theft and may lead to criminal prosecution by Company.\n\nI accept all the terms and conditions mentioned therein. I shall commence my Internship with effect from __________________\n\nName:                                                                             Date:                                                Signature:</div>	/uploads/pdfs/offer_1777438336796.pdf	f	2026-04-29 04:52:17.39	cmoiig32r000461xxy1vwraim	{"ctc": 50000, "dob": "", "pan": "", "city": "t", "date": "2026-04-24", "grat": 943.8405086142617, "mode": "Office", "name": "poorna", "spec": 19622.46379655429, "basic": 19622.4637965543, "email": "m87@gmail.com", "empId": "", "state": "ap", "gender": "Male", "hraPct": "50", "mobile": "234567", "prefix": "Mr.", "reason": "", "refNum": "0005", "aadhaar": "", "address": "t, ap, 356", "contact": "m87@gmail.com", "country": "India", "empType": "Internship", "manager": "", "pinCode": "356", "sigName": "hh", "address1": "", "address2": "", "basicPct": "40", "duration": "3", "exitType": "Resigned", "lastName": "", "location": "", "passport": "", "reviewer": "", "altMobile": "", "firstName": "poorna", "incAmount": "", "includePT": "No", "offerDate": "2026-05-01", "validTill": "2026-04-27", "currentCtc": "", "deductions": "0", "department": "Operations", "employeeId": null, "exitReason": "", "fatherName": "", "includeEPF": "Yes", "includeESI": "Yes", "revisedCtc": "50000", "assetReturn": "Completed", "candidateId": "cmoiig32r000461xxy1vwraim", "designation": "HR Manager", "finalAmount": "0", "gratuityPct": "4.81", "hrClearance": "Yes", "itClearance": "Yes", "joiningDate": "", "offerExpiry": "2026-04-27", "reviewNotes": "