cmnyfjni10002mh347zrfoi60	 Internship Completion Letter	EXPERIENCE	<!-- x-tinymce/html --><p>This is to certify that you have successfully completed your internship as <strong>-designation-</strong> at <strong>-company name-</strong> from <strong>-Date of Join-</strong> to <strong>-effective from(exit date)-</strong>.</p>\n<p>During the period of your internship, you demonstrated a keen interest in learning and were actively involved in the duties and responsibilities assigned to you. Your contributions were valuable, and you showcased strong teamwork, excellent skills, and a commendable aptitude in your area of work.</p>\n<p>We appreciate the effort you put into the tasks assigned and are confident that the experience gained during your time with us will contribute significantly to your future endeavors.</p>\n<p>We wish you the very best in your academic and professional journey ahead.</p>	f			
cmnyfbnv4001518zv5wbcrf0q	 Salary Increment Letter	INCREMENT	<!-- x-tinymce/html --><p>We extend our sincere appreciation for your commendable performance during the evaluation period. Your dedication and exceptional contributions have significantly impacted the success of our organization.</p>\n<p>In recognition of your hard work and commitment, we are pleased to inform you that your compensation will be increased to&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>-CTC-</strong>. This revised annual remuneration will be effective from&nbsp;<strong style="font-size: 0.875rem;">-effective from- </strong><span style="font-size: 0.875rem;">.</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 0.875rem;">For a detailed breakdown of your revised compensation structure, please refer to Annexure-III.</span></p>\n<p>It is important to note that all other terms and conditions outlined in your Offer Letter will remain unchanged.</p>\n<p>Congratulations on your well-deserved success! We look forward to witnessing more exemplary work from you in the future. Your continued dedication and contributions are invaluable to the success of our organization.</p>	t			<!-- x-tinymce/html --><div><b>Note:</b></div><ol>\n<li>For any queries regarding your salary structure please send an email to:<strong>-company email-</strong></li>\n<li>Gratuity is a retirement benefit credited to the employee and eligible as per gratuity policy</li>\n<li>Performance based Incentive is payable monthly after completion of probation. Performance evaluation will be carried out once in 6 months.</li></ol>
cmnyfbnv1001418zv3d4y5gq0	 Employment Confirmation Letter	PROBATION	<!-- x-tinymce/html --><p>We are delighted to formally confirm your employment for the role of&nbsp; <strong>-designation-</strong>, which will commence on <strong>-confirmation date-.</strong></p>\n<p>Your current CTC is&nbsp; <strong>&nbsp;-CTC-</strong></p>\n<p>Enclosed herewith, you will find a comprehensive breakdown of your salary details. It is important to note that your salary will be subject to periodic reviews in accordance with the company's policies related to your role. Any adjustments will be based on your satisfactory performance. The remaining terms and conditions of your employment will remain unchanged.<br><br>Congratulations on this significant step in your career! We eagerly anticipate the valuable contributions you will bring, and we extend our best wishes for success in this new endeavour.</p>	t			<!-- x-tinymce/html --><ol>\n<li>For any queries regarding your salary structure please send an email to:<br><strong>-company email-</strong></li>\n<li>Gratuity is a retirement benefit credited to the employee and eligible as per gratuity policy</li>\n<li>Performance based Incentive is payable monthly after completion of probation. Performance evaluation will be carried out once in 6 months.</li></ol>
cmnyfbnuv001218zvcscb7wq7	Internship Offer Letter	OFFER	Congratulations! We are excited to offer you the opportunity to join our internship program.\n\nThis internship will have an initial duration of <b>-duration-</b> Month(s), commencing on or before <b>-effective_from-</b>, and will conclude on <b>-effective_to-</b>. The extension of this internship or transition to a permanent role will be contingent upon your performance and our business needs.<b>\nStipend:&nbsp;</b><div>-stipend-&nbsp; You will receive a monthly stipend during the duration of your internship, payable at the end of each month.&nbsp;</div><div>Joining Details:\n\nDate of Joining: On or before -effective_from-.\nLocation: -location-.\nDesignation: -designation-\nRequired Documents:\n\nCopy of your highest educational qualification certificate.\nIdentification and address proof (any one of the following: Passport, Aadhar Card, Voter ID).\nTerms of Internship:\n\nTermination: The internship may be terminated by either party with a given notice of 15 days in writing or via email.\nValidity: The internship agreement is valid until the end date specified ( -effective_to- ), with the possibility of renewal or extension based on mutual agreement.\nWe hope that you will find your internship with us enriching and rewarding. We look forward to having you as part of our team and are confident that this will be an exceptional opportunity for professional growth and personal development.&nbsp;Kindly confirm your acceptance of this offer on or before the joining date.\n\nThank you for considering this opportunity, and we eagerly anticipate your affirmative reply.\n\nWith best wishes,\nFor -company name-\n\n-Hr Name-\n-Signatory Designation-\n\nCandidate Undertaking:\n\nI have carefully read and understood the terms and conditions mentioned above.\n\nI acknowledge that while I am working for -company name-, I will take proper care of all company equipment that I am entrusted with. I further understand that upon